subject: College Athletics
Basketball
NCAA Basketball Tournament (Men)
lead_paragraph: The Cougars (19-15) upset No. 25 Texas-El Paso, sending Coach Tom Penders back to the N.C.A.A. tournament for the first time since 1999.
